- Ah...

05:01.402 --> 05:04.670
La mia famiglia americana!

05:04.672 --> 05:06.438
Ah!
- What?

05:06.440 --> 05:07.706
What?

05:07.708 --> 05:09.541
I'm sorry.
Who--who are you?

05:09.543 --> 05:11.043
- La signora barone?

05:11.045 --> 05:12.044
- Uh, yes.

05:12.046 --> 05:14.046
- La signorina barone!

05:14.048 --> 05:15.881
- I'm sorry, I don't...

05:15.883 --> 05:19.084
Oh, this is the letter
that we...Wrote...

05:19.086 --> 05:20.952
Oh, my gosh.

05:20.954 --> 05:23.055
Are--are you
aunt sarina from Italy?

05:23.057 --> 05:25.891
- Aunt sarina!

05:25.893 --> 05:27.659
- Oh, che bella bambina!

05:27.661 --> 05:30.462
Si, la zia sarina!

05:30.464 --> 05:31.663
- What did she say?

05:31.665 --> 05:32.998
- I don't know.
Just hug her.

05:35.468 --> 05:36.635
- Uh, the money,
please, huh?

05:36.637 --> 05:37.636
- Yeah, okay.

05:37.638 --> 05:39.004
- Uh, excuse me.

05:39.006 --> 05:42.774
