06:15.376 --> 06:17.376
Hey. Hello. Hey!

06:17.378 --> 06:18.744
- Oh, hi, ray.

06:18.746 --> 06:19.744
Listen, I've been trying
to call you.

06:19.746 --> 06:21.713
- Hey, ray, you're just in time
for pizza.

06:21.715 --> 06:24.416
- Raimondo! Oh!

06:26.486 --> 06:28.053
- [chuckling]

06:28.055 --> 06:30.522
Who is this?

06:30.524 --> 06:32.557
- It's zia sarina.
- Who?

06:32.559 --> 06:34.092
- Your aunt from Italy.

06:34.094 --> 06:35.560
- What?

06:35.562 --> 06:36.561
- Yeah.

06:36.563 --> 06:37.996
- Why?

06:37.998 --> 06:39.464
- Because you
kind of invited her.

06:39.466 --> 06:40.966
- When?
- The letter.

06:40.968 --> 06:42.434
You said,
"if you're ever in america,

06:42.436 --> 06:43.602
Come and visit us."

06:43.604 --> 06:45.904
- What, so she
hops on a plane?

06:45.906 --> 06:47.506
Well, who does that?

06:47.508 --> 06:51.410
- A person
who cares about family.

06:51.412 --> 06:52.544
Ti posso aiutare.

06:52.546 --> 06:53.545
- Oh, si.
Grazie.

06:53.547 --> 06:55.480
- I don't believe this.

06:55.482 --> 06:57.449
- Per te. Per te.

06:57.451 --> 07:00.685
- Ah, grazie.

07:00.687 --> 07:02.053
Did you know
we had an ancestor

07:02.055 --> 07:03.121
Who was a count?

07:03.123 --> 07:04.656
She said I look
just like him.

07:04.658 --> 07:05.824
That's right.

07:07.894 --> 07:09.961
- Good, great, hey,
why don't we send for him too?

07:09.963 --> 07:12.464
- Oh, ray,
come on, she's family.

07:12.466 --> 07:14.766
- Plus she says the winters
are very cold in Italy,

07:14.768 --> 07:16.535
And the heat's
not so good.

07:16.537 --> 07:17.803
The heat's good here, huh?

07:17.805 --> 07:19.137
Buono riscaldamento?

07:19.139 --> 07:21.173
- Oh, si!

07:21.175 --> 07:22.707
Molto buono.

07:22.709 --> 07:25.444
[laughing]

07:25.446 --> 07:26.778
- Wait, wait.
Where is she staying?

07:26.780 --> 07:27.846
- Here.
- Here?

07:27.848 --> 07:28.846
- She's not going to be
in the way.

07:28.848 --> 07:30.849
I--I put up a cot
in your office for her.

07:30.851 --> 07:34.219
- In my office?

07:34.221 --> 07:36.455
Dad, why can't she stay
at your house, huh?

07:36.457 --> 07:37.956
She's your father's sister.

07:37.958 --> 07:39.624
- We got only the one
extra bedroom.

07:39.626 --> 07:41.159
There's already
a relative in it.

07:41.161 --> 07:45.564
Unless you want to trade.

07:45.566 --> 07:47.466
- Raimondo e molto stanco.

07:47.468 --> 07:49.634
Perche no andate a casa vostra,
mangiarla la pizza?

07:49.636 --> 07:51.536
E ci vendiamo domani, ah?

07:51.538 --> 07:54.139
[all talking at once]

07:59.011 --> 08:00.879
- Did you see that?

08:00.881 --> 08:03.582
She said something,
and they just got up and left.

08:03.584 --> 08:04.916
What did she say?

08:04.918 --> 08:06.785
- I don't know.
How long is she staying?

08:06.787 --> 08:08.820
- As long as she can do that.

08:22.802 --> 08:24.102
- Hey.

08:24.104 --> 08:26.238
Hey. Yep.
Uh...

08:26.240 --> 08:27.706
Wait a minute.
Wait a--ew.

08:27.708 --> 08:30.108
- Oh, scusi.

08:30.110 --> 08:33.545
Non ti preocupare.
Non c'e problema.

08:33.547 --> 08:34.713
- Well...

08:34.715 --> 08:36.948
Dah.

08:36.950 --> 08:38.049
Ah, you're wearing...

08:38.051 --> 08:41.253
Okay.

