I'll go upstairs.

08:43.790 --> 08:45.657
- No, no, no, no.
Tu lavora.

08:45.659 --> 08:47.025
Lavora.
- Yeah, all right.

08:47.027 --> 08:48.793
I'm just gonna be
a few minutes.

08:48.795 --> 08:51.162
Then I'll get out of here.

08:51.164 --> 08:52.564
- Cristo.

08:52.566 --> 08:55.033
[mumbling in italian]

08:55.035 --> 08:57.302
Ooh.

08:57.304 --> 08:58.303
Sono tuoi,

08:58.305 --> 09:00.572
Tutti questi premi?

09:00.574 --> 09:02.240
- Yeah.
Just some...Awards.

09:02.242 --> 09:06.578
- Oh, sono maravigliosi!
Oh!

09:06.580 --> 09:08.280
- Oh, it's just a few awards.
That's all.

09:08.282 --> 09:11.683
- No, ay,
sono molti, molti!

09:11.685 --> 09:14.286
- Okay, molti, molti, molti.

09:14.288 --> 09:16.187
- Oh, e, e questo?

09:16.189 --> 09:17.856
Per che cosa l'ai vinto?

09:17.858 --> 09:19.190
- That's sportswriter
of the year.

09:19.192 --> 09:20.859
- Eh?

09:20.861 --> 09:24.229
- It's scrittore sportivo
dell'anno.

09:24.231 --> 09:26.765
- Scrittore sportivo
dell'anno!

09:26.767 --> 09:27.766
- Yeah. Yes.

09:27.768 --> 09:29.768
- Oh, raimondo!

09:29.770 --> 09:32.304
- Just...New york only.
New york. Uh...

09:32.306 --> 09:34.139
Solamente per new york.

09:34.141 --> 09:35.740
- Nuova york!

09:35.742 --> 09:39.578
