10:41.908 --> 10:43.174
- No, you're not
bothering me.

10:43.176 --> 10:44.843
- It's okay.
I'm all right.

10:44.845 --> 10:46.411
- No, no, no, no.
Lavora, eh?

10:46.413 --> 10:48.013
- All right.
- Eh, lavora.

10:48.015 --> 10:50.982
- Okay, I'll work
just a few minutes.

11:00.192 --> 11:02.327
- Buona notte,

11:02.329 --> 11:05.263
Scrittore famoso.

11:05.265 --> 11:06.264
